<lb ed="X" n="0772a12"/><lb ed="R126" n="0176a02"/><byline cb:type="other">門人明凡　錄</byline>
<lb ed="X" n="0772a13"/><lb ed="R126" n="0176a03"/><byline cb:type="editor">吳興丁元公
